This patch enables the following IPs on stm32mp257f-ev :
  * LTDC
  * LVDS
  * WSVGA LVDS panel (1024x600)
  * Panel backlight
  * Ilitek touchescreen

Signed-off-by: Raphael Gallais-Pou <raphael.gallais-pou@foss.st.com>
